 《当我弥留之际》的蒂姆·兰贝西斯在网上出现与妻子明显紧张争吵的视频后发表讲话https://www.nme.com/news/music/as-i-lay-dyings-tim-lambesis-speaks-out-after-videos-showing-apparent-tense-altercation-with-wife-surface-online- 3816831?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=as-i-lay-dyings-tim-lambesis-speaks-out-after-videos-showing-apparent-tens-altercation-with-wife-surface-onlineLaura Molloy Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:16:51 +0000 Music NewsNews..Metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3816831 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位主唱声称这些片段是他妻子在本周早些时候向她送达离婚文件后的“公开攻击”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/as-i-lay-dyings-tim-lambesis-speaks-out-after-videos-showing-apparent-tense-altercation-with-wife-surface-online-3816831">《我弥留之际》的蒂姆·兰贝西斯 (Tim Lambesis)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首次出现网上显示与妻子发生明显紧张争吵的视频后发表了言论。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/as-i-lay-dying">《我弥留之际》</a>主唱蒂姆·兰贝西斯在网上流传与妻子发生紧张争吵的视频后发表了讲话。</p><p>这两个片段本周早些时候出现在社交媒体上，似乎显示兰贝西斯和他的妻子丹妮在争吵。</p><p>在一段视频中，可以看到兰贝西斯翻转了丹妮坐的桌子。然后，当她起身走开时，他试图拦截她，并在她要求他停下来时反复殴打自己。</p><p>另一段视频似乎显示这对夫妇在卧室里发生争吵——尽管没有音频。兰贝西斯似乎在大喊大叫，反复冲向丹妮的脸并抓住她。然后他开始打自己，然后才注意到相机，拿起相机并把它关掉。</p><p>现在，兰贝西斯做出了回应，指控丹妮实施家庭暴力，并声称她是在本周早些时候丹妮向她提供离婚文件后发起“这些公开攻击”的。 </p><figure id="attachment_3813517" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813517" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3813517 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813517" class="wp-caption-text"> 《当我弥留之际》的蒂姆·兰贝西斯。图片来源：Joey Foley/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在分享给 Instagram 的一份声明中，这位歌手写道：“目前正在对丹尼·诺里斯（原名兰贝西斯）发出限制令和家庭暴力调查。她现在所说的一切都是为了分散人们的注意力，让他们把注意力集中在我自己对这些引起焦虑的互动的不当（但不是非法）反应上。</p><p> “这个女人在三年多的时间里对我进行了殴打和言语/精神虐待，”他声称。 “我昨天采取了急需且迟来的步骤，递交了离婚文件，离开了她。这就是为什么今天有人试图在网上对我进行报复，但与法庭真正关注的焦点相比，这些尝试显得相形见绌。”</p><p>兰贝西斯随后详细介绍了他说将纳入法庭案件的所谓证据，包括丹妮袭击他、用“刀子或剪刀”追赶他的“多个视频”，并要求他删除她对他进行人身攻击的视频。同时威胁采取进一步的暴力行动。</p><p>他还声称，他有丹妮给他的黑眼圈的照片，以及可以证明如果他试图离开这段关系就会受到身体暴力威胁的证人。</p><p>请阅读下面他的完整声明。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DC4keQPSTIQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.